{"tid":943047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳承認西耶路撒冷為以色列首都","createTime":"2018-12-16T09:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T10:29:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a79855c8c64c72d3035aca2276ca61ab703eba7","tid":943047,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T09:07:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181216/20569825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181216%2F20569825&d=Y4d8R6p8H5hgoI%2F12wVRxv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=f2428758\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181216%2F20569825&h=32957816\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181216/20569825</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月16日 <br />\n<br />\n澳承認西耶路撒冷為以色列首都<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181216/large/a905a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181216%2Flarge%2Fa905a.gif&h=3fc6fffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫理森在一外交演說宣佈決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳洲總理莫理森（Scott Morrison）昨日宣佈承認西耶路撒冷為以色列首都，但只會在以巴達成和平協議後，才將大使館從特拉維夫搬至西耶路撒冷，屆時亦會承認東耶路撒冷是巴勒斯坦首都，此前澳洲只會在耶路撒冷設立國防及貿易辦公室，再物色合適的大使館選址。消息激怒印尼和馬來西亞，威脅收回自由貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以巴達協議才搬大使館<br />\n<br />\n「澳洲政府決定承認西耶路撒冷，即以色列國會和許多政府機構的所在地，為以色列首都。」莫理森指此舉是支持中東的「自由民主」，盼能打破以巴僵局，又稱以色列在聯合國被「欺凌」。<br />\n<br />\n他早在10月已放風指或將跟隨美國，將大使館從特拉維夫搬至耶路撒冷，惹來批評指是為了在猶太人口密集的選區保住自由黨議席，豈料補選卻輸給獨立人士，令執政聯盟在眾議院成為少數派。澳洲將於明年5月大選，民調顯示莫理森的民望落後工黨10個百分點。反對派工黨黨魁肖頓指莫理森把政治私利置於國家利益之上，讓澳洲在國際間顯得愚蠢。在澳洲之前，還有俄羅斯、巴拿馬和捷克承認西耶路撒冷為以色列首都，美國則承認整個耶路撒冷是以色列首都。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/法新社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n科索沃建軍　塞爾維亞威脅出兵<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n聯國氣候大會加時談判　分歧未解"},{"pid":"7f781031f8e42931a34d27b5ef0c3cb5f5f54757","tid":943047,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T09:12:48.000Z","msg":"上帝o既子民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75275161dae7a2c63eb2ad38c8ad0e7ff5b1a87","tid":943047,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"岩啦 快d做美國契仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dbab8d8f6dbd05b5f6adc3012c288059536495","tid":943047,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"世界終於回復正軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0452e31ea00ce05d89e7ccc747f62f7c372fe485","tid":943047,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"271ae76786d4a8858521b1738fc138b3c712979c","tid":943047,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"消息激怒印尼和馬來西亞，威脅收回自由貿易協議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點看都係益你地 多過益澳洲"}]}